snippet.title: Vacations - Lavender
snippet.description:
Newcastle four-piece Vacations were recent guests at the Live at Enmore studios. The band brought with them a summery slice of guitar pop, performing their brand new single, Lavender.

Since their 2018 album, Changes, the band have released a steady stream of standalone singles, garnering an ever-increasing audience. The new single is set to appear on their forthcoming album, Forever In Bloom.

The band's indie-pop influences permeated the track, with airy guitar lines, thumping basslines and bubbling rhythms. Vocalist Campbell Burns effortlessly cut through the mix, injecting the song with a shot of energy.

Recorded at Enmore Audio: https://happymag.tv/enmore-audio/
Produced by Happy Mag: https://happymag.tv/
Find out more: https://happymag.tv/watch-vacations-perform-lavender-live-at-enmore/

#vacations #liveatenmore #indierock #lavender
